Link for executable available on google drive

1.Download Oracle VM Box Manager
2.Download hadoopvm.ova (save the path of file)
3.Import Machine (give hadoopvm.ova file path)
4.After Impot Righ Panel will see Ubuntu1
5.Click Start (VM will start)
6.With this multiple frameworkds are installed scala, flume, hive, spark etc.
7.terminal 
start-dfs.sh (this starts distributed file system)
start-yarn.sh (this start resourse manager)
jps (give list of dfs and resource manager process running) this shows hadoop is running fine

GUI for https://localhost:9870/


